balākā bakapaṅktīḥ parigaṇanayaikā dve tisra iti saṅkhyānena nirdiśanto hastena darśayantaḥ siddhāḥ stanitasamaye tvaṅgarjitakāle sotkampāny utkampapūrvakāṇi priyasahacarīṇāṃ saṃbhrameṇāliṅgitāny āsādya | svayaṃ grahaṇāśleṣasukham anubhūyety arthaḥ || tvāṃ mānāyaṣyanti | tvannimittatvāt sukhalābhasyeti bhāvaḥ ||

<commentary>utpaśyāmīti || he sakhe megha, matpriyārthaṃ yathā tathā drutaṃ kṣipram || "laghu kṣipram araṃ drutam" ity amaraḥ || yiyāsor yātum icchor api || yāteḥ sann antād upratyayaḥ || te tava kakubhaiḥ kuṭajakusumaiḥ surabhau sugandhini || "kakubhaḥ kuje 'rjune" iti śabdārṇave || parvate parvate pratiparvatam || vīpsāyāṃ dviruktiḥ || kālakṣepaṃ kālavilambam || "kṣepo vilambe nindāyām" iti viśvaḥ || utpaśyāmy utprekṣe || vilambahetuṃ darśayan nāśugamanaṃ prārthayate—śukleti || sajalāni sānandabāṣpāṇi nayanāni yeṣāṃ taiḥ śuklāpāṅgair mayūraiḥ || "mayūro barhiṇo barhī śuklāpāṅgaḥ śikhāvalaḥ" iti yādavaḥ || kekāḥ svavāṇīḥ || kekā vāṇī mayūrasya" ity amaraḥ || svāgatīkṛtya svāgatavacanīkṛtya pratyudyātaḥ pratyudgataḥ | mayūravāṇīkṛtātithya ity arthaḥ | bhavān katham api yathākathañcid āśu gantuṃ vyavasyed udyuñjīta || prārthane liṅ | "śeṣe prathamaḥ" iti prathamapuruṣaḥ | śeṣaś cāyaṃ bhavacchabdo yuṣmadasmacchabdavyatirekāt || "svāgatīkṛtya kekāḥ" ity atra kekāsvāropyamāṇasya svāgatavañcanasya prakṛtapratyudgamanopayogāt pariṇāmālaṅkāraḥ | tad uktam alaṅkārasarvasve—"āropyamāṇasya prakṛtopayogitve pariṇāmaḥ" iti ||</commentary>

pāṇḍv iti || he megha, tvayy āsanne sanikṛṣṭe sati daśārṇo nāma janapadāḥ sūcibhinnaiḥ sūciṣu mukulāgreṣu bhinnair vikasitaiḥ || "ketakīmukulāgreṣu sūciḥ syāt" iti śabdārṇave || ketakaiḥ ketakīkusumaiḥ pāṇḍucchāyā haritavarṇā upavanānāṃ vṛtayaḥ kaṇṭakaśākhāvaraṇā yeṣu te tathoktāḥ || "prākāro varaṇaḥ sālaḥ prācīraṃ prāntato vṛtiḥ" ity amaraḥ || tathā gṛhabalibhujāṃ kākādigrāmapakṣiṇāṃ nīḍārambhaiḥ kulāya nirmāṇaiḥ ||
